  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And among these people there was one, especially one student, he had a French name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was very antisemitic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we wrote the essay, and this essay was about the loyalty, as I said.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in this essay we wrote that we are the only true ones in this world, the Nazis, you see.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We actually are the ones [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] who are the strongest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we will conquer the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we will conquer even the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And why will you conquer the United States?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they wrote in this essay, because in the United States they have fighting between the races, black and white.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will kill each other, and in the end we will take over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean they wrote all this in the essay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't believe it, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then finally when the school was nearly at its end, and we made the final exam, and the result of the final exam is called Abitur, A-B-I-T-U-R, which is an entrance exam to a university, everyone had to write an essay what they would do afterwards.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wrote, and I told the teacher before, actually this goes back in a way, beginning when the teacher said Jews cannot go on Saturday anymore to school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he asked me, why don't you want to go now?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to him, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since Hitler came to power, the Germans want to be more German 'Nazi' in quotation mark, and I want to be more Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then afterwards at this essay at the end of the school year, I wrote down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still have the outline that's written in German that since there is nothing left over for me in Germany what to do, I cannot do anything else.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
